## ğŸ› ï¸ Configuration

### Basic Configuration

The setup script creates optimized configuration files:

```bash
npm run setup
```

This creates:
- `config/config.json` - Main bot configuration
- `config/discord-config.json` - Discord integration settings

### Manual Configuration

Edit `config/config.json`:

```json
{
  "server": {
    "host": "your-server.com",
    "port": 25565,
    "version": "1.21.4"
  },
  "bot": {
    "username": "YourBot",
    "auth": "offline"
  },
  "features": {
    "autoEat": {
      "enabled": true,
      "priority": "foodPoints",
      "startAt": 14
    },
    "pvp": {
      "enabled": true,
      "autoAttackHostile": true
    },
    "logging": {
      "enabled": true,
      "logChat": true,
      "logCommands": true,
      "logPvP": true
    },
    "webInventory": {
      "enabled": true,
      "port": 3001
    }
  }
}
```

